Delivery Calculation
1. In the admin panel: products section - add a Large Delivery check box field to products and product variations
2. In the admin panel: System Settings - add  large delivery cost fields for Zone 1, Zone 2, Zone 3
3. In the admin panel: System Settings - add  small delivery cost fields for Zone 1, Zone 2, Zone 3
4. Delivery zones will be defined by zip codes found in: artifacts\delivery_Zip_Codes.xlsx
5. In the cart and checkout,
5a. If the user selects same day delivery,
 5a1. If one item in the order is designated a Large Delivery,
5a1a. The user will be charged the large delivery cost for the users zip code zone
5a2. If NO items in the order are designated as Large Delivery,
5a2a. The user will be charged the small delivery cost for the users zip code zone
